verse.lines:
I will celebrate
Sing unto the Lord
Sing to the Lord a new song
I will celebrate

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
With my heart rejoicing within
With my mind focused on Him
With my hands raised to the heavens
All I am worshiping Him
